vdsf -- History of visible changes.

Copyright (C) 2006-2008, Daniel Prevost <dprevost@users.sourceforge.net>
See the end for copying conditions.

Please send vdsf bug reports to dprevost@users.sourceforge.net.
or use the sourceforge tracker for vdsf bug reports at
http://sourceforge.net/tracker/?group_id=156288&atid=799182

Version 0.1

    *   Data components:
          o Folders (to hold the other data components)
          o Hash Maps
          o Queues (FIFO only)
    * Transactions
    * C API
    * Man pages for the C API
    * i18n (internationalization)

Version 0.2

    * C++ API
    * Some crash-recovery features at startup
    * Better isolation policy at startup
    * A pseudo-shell utility (vdssh)
    
-------------------------------------------------------

